Package invaders

Interface Summary
IBehaviour IBehaviour: interface for behaviours.
IBehaviourMgr IBehaviourMgr: implementations manage a set of IBehaviours.
IEnemy IEnemy: all enemy behaviours must implement this.
IPlayer IPlayer: all player behaviours must implement this.
ISpawnable An ISpawnable is an object that can be 'spawned' - ie placed at a specific 'location'.
 

Class Summary
Behaviour Behaviour - implements invader behaviours.
BehaviourMgr BehaviourMgr: a manager of a set of IBehaviours.
BubbleBehaviour BubbleBehaviour - implements movement behaviour for all objects taking the role of 'Bubble'.
InvaderBehaviour InvaderBehaviour - implements movement behaviour for all fish taking the role of 'Invader'.
PlayerBehaviour PlayerBehaviour - implements movement behaviour for the fish taking the role of 'Player'.
